    <bridgehead>Text Editing</bridgehead>

    <para>For details, see <xref linkend="undo-redo" />, <xref
    linkend="entering-text" />, <xref linkend="words" />, <xref
    linkend="lines" /> and <xref linkend="paragraphs" />.</para>

